<br>
And the way you work with them is by *not* attacking their roleplay OOCly. By not making judgment calls and blowing them off. By acting IN CHARACTER and sending a brief OOC tell to say &quot;hey, good to see an RPer here... just wanted to let you know this is all IC.&quot;<br>
<br>
Too many times the &quot;purists&quot; treat alternate forms of RP with OOC disdain. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=roninsenshi>RoninSenshi</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Senshi No Adakia</span><br>  Posts: 1396<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/6/02 5:23:06 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1941.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Shintou3.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_devil.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Work with the Roleplay</span><hr size=1> I'm only hateful cause no one loved me when I was lil ..<br>
